document_data.mainbody:
Tezambrils Street was a road that was located in the city of Waterdeep.
Tezambrils Street was located in the central section of Waterdeeps Southern Ward. The road originated in the north on Robins Way where it branched south to eventually end in a neighborhood in front of Anchorets Court. Tezambrils Street also connected with the Forcebar, Tulmasters Street, and Rednose Alley.
New Moon Swords was located along the east side of Tezambrils Street near Rednose Alley.
